<h1>String Copy and Concatenation</h1><p>
<ul><li><h2><font color=#FFFFCC>Traditional functions strcpy(), strcat() unsafe</font></h2>
<ul><li><font color=#FFFFCC>No count parameter</font>
<li><font color=#FFFFCC>Unbounded src string overflows dest</font>
</ul><li><h2><font color=#FFFFCC></font></h2>
<li><h2><font color=#FFFFCC>Usual advice: use strncpy(), strncat()</font></h2>
<ul><li><font color=#FFFFCC>Additional parameter is a maximum count</font>
</ul><li><h2><font color=#FFFFCC>Inconsistent count parameter semantics</font></h2>
<ul><li><font color=#FFFFCC>strncpy(): size of dest buffer</font>
<li><font color=#FFFFCC>strncat(): number of chars to copy</font>
</ul></ul></body>
